import React from 'react';
import {
  Box, Typography, TextField, Grid, Paper, Table, TableBody, 
  TableCell, TableContainer, TableHead, TableRow, Checkbox, Button
} from '@mui/material';

const ApplicationReportBPT = () => {
  const [formData, setFormData] = React.useState({
    // Advertisement Details
    adNo: '',
    adDate: '',
    applicationNo: '',
    courseName: '',
    courseCode: '',
    dateOfEntry: '',
    lastDate: '',
    department: '',

    // Applicant's Details
    name: '',
    fatherName: '',
    dob: '',
    age: '',
    placeOfBirth: '',
    socialStatus: '',
    nationality: '',
    maritalStatus: '',
    gender: '',
    differentlyAbled: '',
    mark1: '',
    mark2: '',
    universityArea: '',
    inService: '',
    aadhar: '',
    fatherEmail: '',

    // Address Details
    correspondenceAddress: '',
    correspondenceCountry: '',
    correspondenceState: '',
    correspondenceDistrict: '',
    correspondencePincode: '',
    correspondenceMobile: '',
    correspondenceEmail: '',
    sameAsCorrespondence: true,
    permanentAddress: '',
    permanentCountry: '',
    permanentState: '',
    permanentDistrict: '',
    permanentPincode: '',
    permanentMobile: '',
    permanentEmail: '',

    // Parents' Details
    fatherNameParent: '',
    fatherAge: '',
    fatherOccupation: '',
    motherName: '',
    motherAge: '',
    motherOccupation: '',

    // Intermediate Marks
    subjects: [
      { subject: 'Botany', y1: '', y2: '', practical: '', total: '', max: '' },
      { subject: 'Zoology', y1: '', y2: '', practical: '', total: '', max: '' },
      { subject: 'Physics', y1: '', y2: '', practical: '', total: '', max: '' },
      { subject: 'Chemistry', y1: '', y2: '', practical: '', total: '', max: '' },
      { subject: 'English', y1: '', y2: '', practical: '', total: '', max: '' },
      { subject: 'Second Language', y1: '', y2: '', practical: '', total: '', max: '' },
    ],
    totalMarks: '',
    totalPercentage: '',
    groupTotal: '',
    groupPercentage: '',

    // Educational History
    educationHistory: [
      { class: '', year: '', school: '', place: '' },
      { class: '', year: '', school: '', place: '' },
      { class: '', year: '', school: '', place: '' },
      { class: '', year: '', school: '', place: '' },
      { class: '', year: '', school: '', place: '' },
      { class: '', year: '', school: '', place: '' },
      { class: '', year: '', school: '', place: '' },
    ],

    // EAPCET Details
    eapcetRegNo: '',
    hallTicketNo: '',
    rank: '',

    // Payment Details
    paymentType: '',
    transactionId: '',
    paymentDate: '',
    bankName: '',
    branchDetails: '',
    amount: '',
    paymentRemarks: '',

    // Documents
    documents: [
      { id: 1, type: 'CASTE CERTIFICATE' },
      { id: 2, type: '10th Class Marks Memo' },
      { id: 3, type: 'INTERMEDIATE MARKS MEMO' },
      { id: 4, type: '6TH to 10TH Study and Conduct Certificate' },
      { id: 5, type: 'INTER STUDY AND CONDUCT CERTIFICATE' },
      { id: 6, type: 'TRANSFER OR MIGRATION CERTIFICATE of Intermediate' },
      { id: 7, type: 'TELANGANA STATE EXPECT-2025 RANK CARD' },
    ],

    // Declaration
    signature: '',
    declarationDate: '',
    officeRemarks: ''
  });

  const handleChange = (e) => {
    const { name, value } = e.target;
    setFormData(prev => ({
      ...prev,
      [name]: value
    }));
  };

  const handleSubjectChange = (index, field, value) => {
    const updatedSubjects = [...formData.subjects];
    updatedSubjects[index][field] = value;
    setFormData(prev => ({
      ...prev,
      subjects: updatedSubjects
    }));
  };

  const handleEducationChange = (index, field, value) => {
    const updatedEducation = [...formData.educationHistory];
    updatedEducation[index][field] = value;
    setFormData(prev => ({
      ...prev,
      educationHistory: updatedEducation
    }));
  };

  const handleSameAddressChange = (e) => {
    const checked = e.target.checked;
    setFormData(prev => ({
      ...prev,
      sameAsCorrespondence: checked,
      permanentAddress: checked ? prev.correspondenceAddress : '',
      permanentCountry: checked ? prev.correspondenceCountry : '',
      permanentState: checked ? prev.correspondenceState : '',
      permanentDistrict: checked ? prev.correspondenceDistrict : '',
      permanentPincode: checked ? prev.correspondencePincode : '',
      permanentMobile: checked ? prev.correspondenceMobile : '',
      permanentEmail: checked ? prev.correspondenceEmail : ''
    }));
  };

  const handleSubmit = (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    console.log('Form submitted:', formData);
    // Add your form submission logic here
  };

  return (
    <Box component="form" onSubmit={handleSubmit} sx={{ pt: 4, px: 6, pb: 7 }}>
      <Typography variant="h5" gutterBottom align="center">
        APPLICATION FORM - Bachelor of Physiotherapy - 2025
      </Typography>

      <Grid container spacing={3}>
        {/* Advertisement Details */}
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Paper elevation={2} sx={{ p: 2 }}>
            <Typography variant="subtitle1" fontWeight="bold">Advertisement Details</Typography>
            <Grid container spacing={2}>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="adNo" label="Ad. No." fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="adDate" label="Ad. Date" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="applicationNo" label="Application No." fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="courseName" label="Course Name" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="courseCode" label="Course Code" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="dateOfEntry" label="Date of Entry" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="lastDate" label="Last Date of Application" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="department" label="Department" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>

        {/* Applicant's Details */}
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Paper elevation={2} sx={{ p: 2 }}>
            <Typography variant="subtitle1" fontWeight="bold">Applicant's Details</Typography>
            <Grid container spacing={2}>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="name" label="Name" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="fatherName" label="Father's Name" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="dob" label="Date of Birth" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="age" label="Age (on last date)" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="placeOfBirth" label="Place of Birth" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="socialStatus" label="Social Status" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="nationality" label="Nationality" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="maritalStatus" label="Marital Status" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="gender" label="Gender" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="differentlyAbled" label="Differently Abled" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="mark1" label="Identification Mark 1" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="mark2" label="Identification Mark 2" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="universityArea" label="University Area" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="inService" label="In-service (Govt.)" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="aadhar" label="Aadhar" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField name="fatherEmail" label="Father's Email" fullWidth onChange={handleChange} />
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>

        {/* Address Details */}
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Paper elevation={2} sx={{ p: 2 }}>
            <Typography variant="subtitle1" fontWeight="bold">Address Details</Typography>
            
            {/* Correspondence Address */}
            <Box sx={{ mb: 3 }}>
              <Typography variant="subtitle2" fontWeight="bold" gutterBottom>
                Correspondence Address
              </Typography>
              <Grid container spacing={2}>
                <Grid item xs={12}>
                  <TextField 
                    name="correspondenceAddress"
                    label="Address" 
                    fullWidth 
                    multiline
                    rows={2}
                    onChange={handleChange}
                  />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} md={3}>
                  <TextField 
                    name="correspondenceCountry"
                    label="Country" 
                    fullWidth 
                    onChange={handleChange}
                  />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} md={3}>
                  <TextField 
                    name="correspondenceState"
                    label="State" 
                    fullWidth 
                    onChange={handleChange}
                  />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} md={3}>
                  <TextField 
                    name="correspondenceDistrict"
                    label="District" 
                    fullWidth 
                    onChange={handleChange}
                  />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} md={3}>
                  <TextField 
                    name="correspondencePincode"
                    label="Pin Code" 
                    fullWidth 
                    onChange={handleChange}
                  />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} md={3}>
                  <TextField 
                    name="correspondenceMobile"
                    label="Mobile No." 
                    fullWidth 
                    onChange={handleChange}
                  />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} md={3}>
                  <TextField 
                    name="correspondenceEmail"
                    label="E-mail Id" 
                    fullWidth 
                    onChange={handleChange}
                  />
                </Grid>
              </Grid>
            </Box>

            {/* Permanent Address */}
            <Box sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="subtitle2" fontWeight="bold" gutterBottom>
                Permanent Address
              </Typography>
              <Grid container spacing={2}>
                <Grid item xs={12}>
                  <TextField 
                    name="permanentAddress"
                    label="Address" 
                    value={formData.permanentAddress}
                    fullWidth 
                    multiline
                    rows={2}
                    onChange={handleChange}
                    disabled={formData.sameAsCorrespondence}
                  />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} md={3}>
                  <TextField 
                    name="permanentCountry"
                    label="Country" 
                    value={formData.permanentCountry}
                    fullWidth 
                    onChange={handleChange}
                    disabled={formData.sameAsCorrespondence}
                  />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} md={3}>
                  <TextField 
                    name="permanentState"
                    label="State" 
                    value={formData.permanentState}
                    fullWidth 
                    onChange={handleChange}
                    disabled={formData.sameAsCorrespondence}
                  />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} md={3}>
                  <TextField 
                    name="permanentDistrict"
                    label="District" 
                    value={formData.permanentDistrict}
                    fullWidth 
                    onChange={handleChange}
                    disabled={formData.sameAsCorrespondence}
                  />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} md={3}>
                  <TextField 
                    name="permanentPincode"
                    label="Pin Code" 
                    value={formData.permanentPincode}
                    fullWidth 
                    onChange={handleChange}
                    disabled={formData.sameAsCorrespondence}
                  />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} md={3}>
                  <TextField 
                    name="permanentMobile"
                    label="Mobile No." 
                    value={formData.permanentMobile}
                    fullWidth 
                    onChange={handleChange}
                    disabled={formData.sameAsCorrespondence}
                  />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={6} md={3}>
                  <TextField 
                    name="permanentEmail"
                    label="E-mail Id" 
                    value={formData.permanentEmail}
                    fullWidth 
                    onChange={handleChange}
                    disabled={formData.sameAsCorrespondence}
                  />
                </Grid>
              </Grid>
            </Box>

            {/* Checkbox for same address */}
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center' }}>
              <Checkbox 
                checked={formData.sameAsCorrespondence} 
                onChange={handleSameAddressChange} 
              />
              <Typography variant="body2">Same as Correspondence Address</Typography>
            </Box>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>

        {/* Parent/Spouse Details */}
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Paper elevation={2} sx={{ p: 2 }}>
            <Typography variant="subtitle1" fontWeight="bold">Parents' Details</Typography>
            <Grid container spacing={2}>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <TextField 
                  name="fatherNameParent"
                  label="Father's Name" 
                  fullWidth 
                  onChange={handleChange}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <TextField 
                  name="fatherAge"
                  label="Age" 
                  fullWidth 
                  onChange={handleChange}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <TextField 
                  name="fatherOccupation"
                  label="Occupation" 
                  fullWidth 
                  onChange={handleChange}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <TextField 
                  name="motherName"
                  label="Mother's Name" 
                  fullWidth 
                  onChange={handleChange}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <TextField 
                  name="motherAge"
                  label="Age" 
                  fullWidth 
                  onChange={handleChange}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <TextField 
                  name="motherOccupation"
                  label="Occupation" 
                  fullWidth 
                  onChange={handleChange}
                />
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>

        {/* Intermediate Marks */}
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Paper elevation={2} sx={{ p: 2 }}>
            <Typography variant="subtitle1" fontWeight="bold" gutterBottom>Intermediate Marks (Telangana State)</Typography>
            <Grid container spacing={1}>
              {formData.subjects.map((item, index) => (
                <React.Fragment key={index}>
                  <Grid item xs={2}>
                    <TextField 
                      label="Subject" 
                      value={item.subject} 
                      fullWidth 
                      InputProps={{ readOnly: true }}
                    />
                  </Grid>
                  <Grid item xs={1.5}>
                    <TextField 
                      label="1st Year" 
                      value={item.y1}
                      onChange={(e) => handleSubjectChange(index, 'y1', e.target.value)}
                      fullWidth 
                    />
                  </Grid>
                  <Grid item xs={1.5}>
                    <TextField 
                      label="2nd Year" 
                      value={item.y2}
                      onChange={(e) => handleSubjectChange(index, 'y2', e.target.value)}
                      fullWidth 
                    />
                  </Grid>
                  {['Botany', 'Zoology', 'Physics', 'Chemistry'].includes(item.subject) && (
                    <Grid item xs={1.5}>
                      <TextField 
                        label="Practical" 
                        value={item.practical}
                        onChange={(e) => handleSubjectChange(index, 'practical', e.target.value)}
                        fullWidth 
                      />
                    </Grid>
                  )}
                  {!['Botany', 'Zoology', 'Physics', 'Chemistry'].includes(item.subject) && (
                    <Grid item xs={1.5}>
                      <TextField 
                        label="Practical" 
                        value="-" 
                        fullWidth 
                        InputProps={{ readOnly: true }}
                      />
                    </Grid>
                  )}
                  <Grid item xs={2}>
                    <TextField 
                      label="Total" 
                      value={item.total}
                      onChange={(e) => handleSubjectChange(index, 'total', e.target.value)}
                      fullWidth 
                    />
                  </Grid>
                  <Grid item xs={2}>
                    <TextField 
                      label="Max Marks" 
                      value={item.max}
                      onChange={(e) => handleSubjectChange(index, 'max', e.target.value)}
                      fullWidth 
                    />
                  </Grid>
                </React.Fragment>
              ))}
            </Grid>

            <Box mt={2}>
              <TextField 
                name="totalMarks"
                label="Total Marks" 
                fullWidth 
                sx={{ mb: 1 }} 
                onChange={handleChange}
              />
              <TextField 
                name="totalPercentage"
                label="Total Percentage" 
                fullWidth 
                sx={{ mb: 1 }} 
                onChange={handleChange}
              />
              <TextField 
                name="groupTotal"
                label="Group Total" 
                fullWidth 
                sx={{ mb: 1 }} 
                onChange={handleChange}
              />
              <TextField 
                name="groupPercentage"
                label="Group Percentage" 
                fullWidth 
                onChange={handleChange}
              />
            </Box>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>

        {/* Educational History */}
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Paper elevation={2} sx={{ p: 2 }}>
            <Typography variant="subtitle1" fontWeight="bold" gutterBottom>Educational History</Typography>
            <Grid container spacing={2}>
              {formData.educationHistory.map((item, index) => (
                <React.Fragment key={index}>
                  <Grid item xs={3}>
                    <TextField 
                      label="Class" 
                      value={item.class}
                      onChange={(e) => handleEducationChange(index, 'class', e.target.value)}
                      fullWidth 
                    />
                  </Grid>
                  <Grid item xs={2}>
                    <TextField 
                      label="Year" 
                      value={item.year}
                      onChange={(e) => handleEducationChange(index, 'year', e.target.value)}
                      fullWidth 
                    />
                  </Grid>
                  <Grid item xs={4}>
                    <TextField 
                      label="School" 
                      value={item.school}
                      onChange={(e) => handleEducationChange(index, 'school', e.target.value)}
                      fullWidth 
                    />
                  </Grid>
                  <Grid item xs={3}>
                    <TextField 
                      label="Place" 
                      value={item.place}
                      onChange={(e) => handleEducationChange(index, 'place', e.target.value)}
                      fullWidth 
                    />
                  </Grid>
                </React.Fragment>
              ))}
            </Grid>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>

        {/* EAPCET Info */}
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Paper elevation={2} sx={{ p: 2 }}>
            <Typography variant="subtitle1" fontWeight="bold">EAPCET Details</Typography>
            <Grid container spacing={2}>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <TextField 
                  name="eapcetRegNo"
                  label="TG EAPCET Reg No" 
                  fullWidth 
                  onChange={handleChange}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <TextField 
                  name="hallTicketNo"
                  label="Hall Ticket No" 
                  fullWidth 
                  onChange={handleChange}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <TextField 
                  name="rank"
                  label="Rank" 
                  fullWidth 
                  onChange={handleChange}
                />
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>

        {/* Payment Details */}
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Paper elevation={2} sx={{ p: 2 }}>
            <Typography variant="subtitle1" fontWeight="bold">Payment Details</Typography>
            <Grid container spacing={2}>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <TextField 
                  name="paymentType"
                  label="Payment Type" 
                  fullWidth 
                  onChange={handleChange}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <TextField 
                  name="transactionId"
                  label="Transaction ID" 
                  fullWidth 
                  onChange={handleChange}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <TextField 
                  name="paymentDate"
                  label="Payment Date" 
                  fullWidth 
                  onChange={handleChange}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <TextField 
                  name="bankName"
                  label="Bank Name" 
                  fullWidth 
                  onChange={handleChange}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <TextField 
                  name="branchDetails"
                  label="Branch Details" 
                  fullWidth 
                  onChange={handleChange}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={4}>
                <TextField 
                  name="amount"
                  label="Amount (Rs.)" 
                  fullWidth 
                  onChange={handleChange}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={12}>
                <TextField 
                  name="paymentRemarks"
                  label="Remarks" 
                  fullWidth 
                  onChange={handleChange}
                />
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>

        {/* Document Details */}
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Paper elevation={2} sx={{ p: 2 }}>
            <Typography variant="subtitle1" fontWeight="bold">Document Details</Typography>
            <TableContainer>
              <Table>
                <TableHead>
                  <TableRow>
                    <TableCell>S.No.</TableCell>
                    <TableCell>Document Type</TableCell>
                  </TableRow>
                </TableHead>
                <TableBody>
                  {formData.documents.map((doc) => (
                    <TableRow key={doc.id}>
                      <TableCell>{doc.id}</TableCell>
                      <TableCell>{doc.type}</TableCell>
                    </TableRow>
                  ))}
                </TableBody>
              </Table>
            </TableContainer>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>

        {/* Declaration */}
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Paper elevation={2} sx={{ p: 2 }}>
            <Typography variant="subtitle1" fontWeight="bold">Declaration</Typography>
            <Typography paragraph>
              I declare that the particulars given above are correct. I agree to abide by the admission prospectus issued by the Institute. I also declare that in the event that information provided is incorrect or false. I may be prosecuted as per law.
            </Typography>
            <Grid container spacing={2}>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField 
                  name="signature"
                  label="Signature" 
                  fullWidth 
                  onChange={handleChange}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={6}>
                <TextField 
                  name="declarationDate"
                  label="Date" 
                  fullWidth 
                  onChange={handleChange}
                />
              </Grid>
              <Grid item xs={12}>
                <TextField 
                  name="officeRemarks"
                  label="Remarks (For office use only)" 
                  fullWidth 
                  onChange={handleChange}
                />
              </Grid>
            </Grid>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>

        {/* Submit Button */}
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <Button 
            type="submit" 
            variant="contained" 
            color="primary" 
            size="large"
            fullWidth
          >
            Submit Application
          </Button>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default ApplicationReportBPT;
